Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:07.02,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:09.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In this kingdom where magic is everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:12.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,there is one boy who can't use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:15.61,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:18.93,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,With guts and hard work, \Nhe made it into the Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:21.75,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and he never gave up, \Ndespite how much he got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:24.62,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He continues to diligently aim for the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.79,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you are a peasant,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:29.63,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,or even if you're poor...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:32.38,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone in this world can still shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:34.80,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He's working hard to prove that,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:37.78,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and to become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.64,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,To defeat the devil Megicula, \Nwho inhabits the Spade Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:46.31,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and the others have been training hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:49.32,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Dragon's Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:51.86,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral Flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:56.56,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen of the Heart Kingdom, Loropechika, \Nwho had been cursed by Megicula,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:58.17,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,gave them six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:03.05,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In that span of time, Asta and the\N others must surpass their limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:09.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:13.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:16.55,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Well done on your training, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:19.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:21.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:23.43,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:27.44,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually cursed, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:29.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.14,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're not actually cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:33.48,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You just have an incurable \Ncase of girl-craziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:37.24,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle! You're as beautiful as ever tod— er...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:39.62,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly the part you need to fix, Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.09,0:01:41.16,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.09,0:01:42.63,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That! That! That! That!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:42.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:45.25,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:47.21,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:49.08,flashback,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,You're cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:49.88,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:52.30,flashback,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,You're a hopeless playboy who hits \Non any woman in your path!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:58.97,sign_9601_108_Playboy,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz28\fscx175\pos(146,140)\fscy175\fad(100,1)}Playboy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:53.70,flashbacktop,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,P-Playboy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:53.70,flashback,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,All that running away and trying
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:55.86,flashback,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,to act cool made you a bigger \Nfailure than you already were!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:58.97,sign_9669_112_Failure,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz9\pos(482,61)\fscx175\fscy175}Failure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:55.86,flashbacktop,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:58.97,flashback,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,And once you pick up bad habits, \Nthey won't be easy to break!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:01:58.97,sign_9747_115_Bad_Habits,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-4.89\pos(510,235)}Bad Habits
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:58.97,flashbacktop,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad habits?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:02.93,flashback,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,How could someone like you with so \Nmany faults make Miss Finnes happy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:04.68,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.05,0:02:09.12,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I already have my heart set on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:12.02,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let this curse plague me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:16.36,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I won't be able to make \NMiss Finnes happy, just like Langris said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:19.50,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the person Captain Yami mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:24.83,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought Finral could \Nbe so serious about someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:26.59,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:28.34,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I need to defeat this curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:31.83,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,so join me in training to \Nmake my heart stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:33.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:36.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:38.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:42.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's beat this curse out of you \Nso you can be the man she deserves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:43.20,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:46.78,italicstop,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Training to make his heart stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:47.93,sign_4757_29_Royal_Capital__M,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(737,1)}The Dreavy Hinker
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:49.94,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:52.44,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's a damn mixer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:17.82,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,1871)\t(210,2419,\fscx120\fscy120)}The One Who Has My Heart,\N My Mind, and Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:31.75,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea! Apparently mixers\N make your heart stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:34.89,italicstop,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I really hope I get to fight this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:38.65,sign_5790_50_Mereoleona_Vermi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(259,790)}Rebecca Scarlet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:39.63,italicstop,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,To think that Asta would invite me to \Na mixer... I wonder what brought this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.59,italics,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to complain \Nabout the chance, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:45.78,sign_5790_50_Mereoleona_Vermi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(251,787)}Karen Lapis
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:46.26,italicstop,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,When the heck did Rebecca get so \Nfriendly with the Magic Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.31,italics,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to get married already.\NI don't even care who it's with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:53.54,sign_5790_50_Mereoleona_Vermi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(259,790)}Eliza Zakkeroni
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.75,italicstop,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in real men.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:55.11,italicstop,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,I only showed up because I was invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:57.83,italics,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to go back home \Nand read the rest of my novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:00.34,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be rude if I didn't try \Nto sweet-talk these women
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:02.10,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,on this battlefield known as a "mixer."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:04.49,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, it's the perfect training for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:07.11,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I will do my absolute best \Nto overcome this curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:11.73,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Training? Please. I almost \Nchanged my mind about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:14.85,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing I came \Nalong because I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:17.37,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But wait, what am I even worried about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:19.25,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, you've got something on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:26.66,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:30.97,main,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, stop! You're going to bring our \Nshop down in more ways than one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.11,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Silence, you puny insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:35.73,main,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I bother hiring you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:39.98,main,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, break anything else \Nin here, and you're fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:46.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Nero! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.07,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Just because.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.99,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Just because?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:52.60,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have you underestimating \Nthe work of a waitress—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:56.87,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's actually really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:06:01.63,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,If Asta sees Nero looking this cute, \Nhe might end up f-f-f-f-f-f-fa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:02.78,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:07.60,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to go check out Asta's table. \NYou take care of the other ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:11.65,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why am I trying to keep Nero and Asta apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:14.47,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter to me one bit \Nwho Asta falls in love with!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.10,main,Guy customer,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, missy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.77,main,Guy customer,0000,0000,0000,,Get me another beer, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.81,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Fetch it yourself, you insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.90,main,Guy customer,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're the girl from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:23.82,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:27.40,main,Guy customer,0000,0000,0000,,A-An angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:32.45,main,asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing? It's your \Nturn to introduce yourself, Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:35.68,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just came here to eat today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:36.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:39.34,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... I just wanted \Nto enjoy some quiet time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:41.53,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,but you two had to drag me out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:42.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:46.84,italics,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes... There's always \Nat least one clueless guy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.72,italics,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,who thinks this is the cool thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:53.66,italics,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure he was the \Ngaudiest one at our last mixer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:57.05,main,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,B-But since we're all enjoying a meal together,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:07:00.22,main,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to hear about you \Nbeing a Magic Knight, Finral—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:03.62,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... that's not my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:05.36,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's{\i0} not your thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.93,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,This hurts so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:12.49,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,A girl is actually interested, \Nand having to ignore her is just torture!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:16.13,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But this is all part of my training, \Ntraining, training!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:17.13,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hurgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:20.54,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,M-My right hand is desperately trying to give \Nher some flowers like I usually would.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:23.47,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Calm yourself, right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:27.55,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Curses! It's just in my very \Nnature to try to hit on girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.92,italics,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,What is this guy trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:35.79,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see! Finral's doing his absolute \Nbest to battle his curse right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:37.93,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when we're gonna start fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:40.26,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like things might be okay after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:43.10,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,My bad! Sorry I'm late, bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:49.82,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I've been {\i1}super{\i0} busy lately. I mean, \Nthis kingdom was in peril just the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:53.98,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really talk about it since \Nit's top secret, bah-hanestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:57.33,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm the one who saved everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:57.33,sign_19264_241___Lies__,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(760,1)}< Lies >
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:08:01.58,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm the one who fixed all \Nthe Magic Knights that went crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:05.58,sign_19264_241___Lies__,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(775,1)}< Lies >
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:05.58,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time until \Nthey make me a captain, bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:09.05,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! It's such a pain, but it's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:13.34,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the king has \Ntaken quite a liking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.34,sign_19264_241___Lies__,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(759,1)}< This is true >
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:17.35,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops. I just said it was top secret, \Nbut I think I might've said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:23.91,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,And you were reading a dirty \Nmagazine again during all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:26.10,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,though I can't say much more. Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.51,main,Phati,0000,0000,0000,,You clearly just told her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:32.28,main,Aphro,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious guy is always more charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:35.59,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I see they're putting on their \Nhellish display of a mixer again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:35.59,top,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, of course! Sorry, it just slipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.98,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What was his name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:40.25,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,According to the guys who \Nwent to the Heart Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:44.05,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,apparently there's some secret \Nbehind my bronze magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:48.53,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief! It looks like I'm the \Nonly guy who can save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:52.21,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to scare even myself, bah-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:55.47,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. His name's Bah-ha-ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:59.47,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,You there! Bring us some \Nmore drinks, bah-hay-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:05.94,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,But I was really shocked when I \Nread that article about you, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:08.77,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it was some kind of mistake, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:13.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it wasn't totally a mistake. \NThey are planning to execute me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:15.42,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,E-Execute you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:16.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's not a huge deal, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:19.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry about it, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:22.92,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so you came to this mixer \Nto get stronger, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:24.54,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:28.91,italics,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wh-What's he talking about? \NIs "fight" some kind of code word?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:32.22,main,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think we should get to \Nknow each other better first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.05,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:36.77,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna have some fun \Nconversations with girls, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:39.95,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, what are you saying, Finral?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:43.06,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I haven't tried \Nto pick up a girl once yet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.37,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,makes this training a huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:51.90,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, I do feel bad for \Nthe girls who actually showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:54.38,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need to explain everything \Nand apologize later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:55.27,main,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:56.07,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:59.45,main,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,My ideal partner actually exists in real life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.58,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:06.48,main,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Take these to table 3— \NW-Wait, you gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:15.65,italics,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,That other one never works, \Nbut this girl has what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:22.18,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:27.18,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he from the Golden Dawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.42,main,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.09,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.86,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:43.49,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Girls from the Blue Rose Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:46.02,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for wait—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:51.54,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain of the Blue Rose Knights... \NAnd the Captain of the Black Bulls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:54.28,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Does this have to do with the \Ninvestigation of the devils?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:08.48,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate my knights holding \Nthis dinner party for me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:13.09,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This is great. It's even better knowing \Nthe Blue Rose Knights are paying for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:17.44,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that again! \NAnyway, I wonder where Asta went!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:19.61,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I was totally gonna invite him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:23.62,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Did they really just come here to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:26.48,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that this was supposed \Nto be a dinner party,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:29.89,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,but seeing how we're lined up, and seeing \NCaptain Charlotte all dressed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.62,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,This is totally a mixer, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:34.77,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a blast today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.75,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please take it easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:43.00,italics,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,I want Sis to be happy, but I don't \Nwant a guy stealing Sis away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:45.76,italics,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck am I supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:48.88,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna get a stomachache \Nif you eat that fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:51.48,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business, Funglasquent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:55.19,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Again, stop trying to abbreviate \N"Funny Glasses Delinquent," you giant woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.52,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually worried about you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:00.86,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:02.74,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:07.24,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,This calls for an eating contest, Glasquent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:11.25,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bring it on, Giant Woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:15.63,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this dress show too much skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:18.36,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,No, I need to believe in Puli's advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:23.88,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Member of the Blue Rose Knights and a \N4th Class Junior Magic Knight, Puli Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:27.01,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,She actually has another side\N to her personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:31.73,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Countless Magic Knights have gone \Nto her for relationship advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:34.83,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Puli was acting as a Cupid, or rather,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:36.86,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,an angel of love, just as her name suggests,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.73,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and saving poor lambs lost\Nin their quest to find love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:42.65,italics,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,You're more beautiful today \Nthan ever, Captain Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:46.24,italics,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami doesn't stand a chance \Nagainst how sexy you look right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:50.32,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,My knights are working so hard to support me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.53,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:55.50,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Prickly Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:58.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you must be\N really cold in that dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:05.09,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear that from a man who \Nwears nothing but underwear and a robe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:07.84,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't underwear! \NThese are my dress clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:13.60,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I know Yami is like this, so I'm embarrassed \Nthat I ever expected anything more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:17.99,italics,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,I had heard how dense he was,\N but this is really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:21.23,italics,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,We need to hold an emergency meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:26.53,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I'm such a \Nspineless captain, Puli.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:29.22,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! We've only just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:30.54,main,Knight A,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Charlotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:31.78,main,Knight B,0000,0000,0000,,You've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.02,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:38.29,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the Black Bulls' captain \Nprefers the prim and proper type.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:39.34,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fix you up in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:41.46,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! What I'm wearing now is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:46.43,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,It's not! You need to be more aggressive \Nin making yourself appealing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:47.72,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,A-Appealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:51.97,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,First, you're going to show him you can be \Nconsiderate by getting some food for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:54.22,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,When a huge plate of food arrives,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:56.57,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,immediately get some for him and serve him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:14:00.06,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of kindness \Nthat'll grab his heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:03.89,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,What's important here is your desire \Nto do something for the one you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:05.32,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:08.20,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Next, a good listener is always attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:12.20,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great to have someone \Nlisten to you talk about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:15.58,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you let them keep \Ntalking until they're satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:18.70,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Your responses can be whatever, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:23.73,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, really? I had no idea! Wow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:26.72,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how this works? I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:31.30,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the most important thing! \NThe most important technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.47,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:36.73,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,It's to nonchalantly touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:40.72,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,T...Touch... him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:45.07,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nope, nope, nope! Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.37,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:50.65,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Serving his food and listening to him \Nis just 10% of how to get a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:52.67,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,The other 90% relies on touching them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:54.16,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot relying on touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:58.12,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use... There's no way I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.98,main,Knight A,0000,0000,0000,,You can do this, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:02.00,main,Knight B,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to let your rival beat you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.48,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:11.94,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,The Blue Rose Knights are with you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:14.55,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.32,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:21.31,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to touch Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:24.07,main,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,Master Finral, you're so cool and apathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:27.03,main,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like the Magic Knight Fiorel\Nfrom the novel I'm reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:28.96,main,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,He's the ultimate Magic \NKnight who can use light,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:31.64,main,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,dark, flame, wind, water, \Nand earth magic, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:32.96,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too many attributes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:33.95,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of novel is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:37.66,main,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,So, um... Are you a strong fighter, Luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.11,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I can show you personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:42.17,italics,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, my. Isn't he being a bit forward?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:45.61,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, the Heart Kingdom \Nsounds really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:46.63,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to go see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:50.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! I'll take you there once \Neverything's taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We'll even take your siblings!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:55.73,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously can't let my \Nguard down around that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:58.14,italics,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,I really need to just fire her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:00.39,italics,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:04.93,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I-I really only have friends \Nin the Black Bulls,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:08.62,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,so it'd make me really happy if we could \Nget to know each other, Miss Puli.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:11.17,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I really love to make dolls,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:14.44,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,so I hope you don't mind if \NI make one of you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:19.45,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'd be honored! I guess I should \Ngive you my measurements, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:20.41,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:24.54,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I've got Coach Charmy on my side! \NLike hell I'm going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:28.75,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly touching Yami \Nis far too difficult for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:31.21,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,F-First, I should try to get him some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.28,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.39,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:40.64,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to get him some food,\N but he beat me to the punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:44.01,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You sure did take your sweet \Ntime powdering your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:46.25,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Bet you're starving now \Nthat you've let it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:51.57,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what happened! I was talking \Nwith my squad members, and it took a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:56.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Yeah, I've been seeing your \Nsquad members everywhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:17:00.20,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,You knew? Wait, of course you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:03.02,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they tagged along \Nbecause they were worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:05.33,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Because you sure can't hold your liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:09.21,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,That's not— er, I guess \Nyou're not totally wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:14.65,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Even when they're not on missions, \Nmy squad members try to support me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:19.06,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,They're also the ones who planned \Nthis dinner party tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:23.40,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I only ever think about fighting \Nand forget about everything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:26.61,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,So I end up relying on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:30.23,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'm supposed to listen, \Nnot keep blabbering on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:35.57,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. As long as you're \Nfiguring out how to rely on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:42.93,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, look at me. Whenever I shi—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:46.66,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, powder my nose, I get my \Nminion to use his spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.50,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You should do that on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:52.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You know, that meat there... It's great \Nwith a bit of pepper sprinkled on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:53.86,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:07.04,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Our hands just nonchalantly touched...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:08.92,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Yami's hand j-just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:17.46,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:18.36,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:22.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really have to act like you \Ngot touched by the biggest germ ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:24.20,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:26.37,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's what just happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.87,main,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to know how amazing \NFiorel is, Master Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:33.94,main,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we have a reading party? \NIn my room, you know, alone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:38.13,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay. I'm not \Ninterested in that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:45.14,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Why, of all times, did a girl who might \Nactually like me show up at this mixer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:47.69,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare touch her, Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:52.15,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Once you touch her, you're finished! \NYou're going to end up sweet-talking her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:55.65,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Resist, Finral! Resist! Resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:59.57,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I'm jealous. Looks like Finral's \Nalready fighting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:03.10,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,We should fight, too! \NLike, right here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.51,main,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Right here and now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:07.66,main,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do I look like such a floozy to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:09.77,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Resist, resist, resist, resist, resist, resist,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.75,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,resist, resist, resist, resist, resist, resist,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.42,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,resist, Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.76,italics,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,Finral seems to be in a lot of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:24.73,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Charlotte?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:27.97,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful lady's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:34.69,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Captain Charlotte. \NYou're more beautiful than ev—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:41.21,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I know I just saved you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:44.51,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't have a single \Nulterior motive in mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:47.58,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Because my heart already \Nbelongs to someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.03,italics,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:50.25,italics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:54.79,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like everybody's having fun down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:58.59,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you plan on holding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:05.43,main,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. My ideal gentleman \Njust doesn't exist in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:08.75,main,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,After dealing with how aggressive \Nyou are, I realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:13.21,main,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,I was ready to marry anyone, \Nbut I was clearly rushing into things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:14.29,main,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:18.49,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... I came to check on \Nhim since he said he'd figured out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:21.37,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,how to train to get over his curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:25.89,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,but it was apparently all a farce. \NI'm sorry for wasting your time, Miss Finnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:30.81,main,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you for bringing me here, Langris.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.94,main,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,It appears Finral does fancy the ladies,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:39.05,main,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,but I believe that's just \Nanother part of his kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:42.97,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true. He's just a \Ngood-for-nothing, girl-crazy loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.79,0:20:45.54,main,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:48.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So you two were here, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:50.65,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What a coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:51.64,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,A coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:54.08,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course it's a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.85,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,You should be a little more honest with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:58.87,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Asta is insanely dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:03.38,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? Wha?! Th-There's nothing \Nthat I want to say to Stupidsta!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:08.90,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Asta. After I dragged \Nyou here to help me with my training,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:10.97,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I just keep striking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:14.20,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never be able to face Miss Finnes like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:18.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Your training's just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:20.28,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:24.22,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that sure was a piece of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:28.76,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you think about guys \Nlike Finral, Prickly Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:32.88,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,No man could possibly move my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:35.69,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Because someone has already claimed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.43,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.43,0:21:38.23,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:44.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You always did say that \Nyour work was your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.04,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Hngh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:48.11,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You okay there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.62,0:21:53.12,italics,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you still need the angel's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:21:59.05,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:02.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's both do our \Nbest these next six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.26,0:22:05.55,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:44.11,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Asta just keeps getting braver,\N and I seem to have more rivals,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:46.36,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not going to give up just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:50.90,main,Some,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, \NPage 136: "A Black Deep-Sea Story."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.57,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 136\N\N{\fs18}A Black Deep-Sea Story
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:53.95,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Kahono? Wait, another rival?!
